{"tid":1610523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位兄弟要有心理準備，短期之內或將會有手足戰死沙場！","createTime":"2019-10-01T17:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T05:22:10.000Z","uid":219007,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b6feff567a7e285b38a302f43b25f5779b7b2e","tid":1610523,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:55:04.000Z","msg":"用常理去推斷 <br />\n<br />\n就當你代入係狗<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;我哋俾人迫害左咁多個月，日日出街俾人鬧，連收工都唔敢自己一個，而今次開完實彈射冧一隻曱甴，行內人個個當我係英雄，連老細都保我地。 依家就係有伙記肯踏出第一步，衝破樽頸位，嚟緊要到我地啦！！&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n佢哋一定有人係咁諗，照常理推敲嚟緊開始實彈就會行常出現<br />\n<br />\n抗爭點都要繼續，但各位要有心理準備會有手足戰死沙場！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光服香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37efe1ef532d61ea67dc2c6112a82f8594296c2","tid":1610523,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b87fda4af1b043fabe0e1a631d0b1de753f5453","tid":1610523,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:57:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bb5afaaccb16bdaf8a2bead40795170cb0ede081","tid":1610523,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:57:14.000Z","msg":"請全民無&middot;限&middot;期罷工罷課，救自己、救義士！迫政府讓步！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，今日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協，答應五大訴求為止！</span>"},{"pid":"7cd89073aed545f4231a0ca43a5b8283b8c6b70d","tid":1610523,"uid":145230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:58:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f81e38bbe8e2b7e55bb1f6c25d5c92fc214663a3","tid":1610523,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:59:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1d497d98bf636347bb9c5ddbaae4c6f74bdf3cc6","tid":1610523,"uid":205378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:59:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">麻煩有時間入黎睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n【長文】✰✰ 一個港島街坊有野想同今日港島班前線講 ✰✰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610354\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610354</a>"},{"pid":"2c118ef5cb1e4411e8f8d01ff956a1c052bd8b6d","tid":1610523,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b8eef5dfc99d897d51964168161b98b86c718a","tid":1610523,"uid":273807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:01:27.000Z","msg":"收聲啦 噏乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f95631082e534972ed9f2226abed832fdf2012","tid":1610523,"uid":282980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97b8eef5dfc99d897d51964168161b98b86c718a","tid":1610523,"uid":273807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:01:27.000Z","msg":"收聲啦 噏乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:03:31.000Z","msg":"常理推斷，佢無講錯喎"},{"pid":"028d918eee397992c334cbf9f14646d5e95c8378","tid":1610523,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97b8eef5dfc99d897d51964168161b98b86c718a","tid":1610523,"uid":273807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:01:27.000Z","msg":"收聲啦 噏乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/